    "name": "赤海狂盗：卡牌远征",
    "steam_appid": 3200220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ: 195899370</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/1d472d2d4258d81bbd71af396416afdc.apng?t=1769466649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/1d472d2d4258d81bbd71af396416afdc.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=618 height=156 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《赤海狂盗：卡牌远征》</strong>是一款 roguelike 策略游戏，玩家将在游戏中操控海盗船长及其船员。驾驶船只穿梭于群岛险恶的水域，与盘踞其中的不法之进行交互。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/27bc083057a7b1ff491d4dbf064fb7d0.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" width=720 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/27bc083057a7b1ff491d4dbf064fb7d0.webm?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/27bc083057a7b1ff491d4dbf064fb7d0.mp4?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的决策将影响各类事件的结果及整体剧情的走向。在不断变幻的地图上从一座岛屿航行至另一座岛屿，使每局游戏都独一无二。通过结合卡牌构筑与船员及船只系统管理的战斗机制，守住自己的声誉并扩大战利品。鼓起勇气，加入赤海狂盗的传奇之旅吧！                           </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                               </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/f7274bf3f3d1f33ba1e4daeb3532d6f3.webp?t=1769466649\" width=724 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>解锁舰队：</strong></i>获取新的船只并解锁阵营，从而得以运用多样化的策略，智取怀特上将让人畏惧的舰队。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                                                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/9bf3c42044d1424e7f51002fce2c7acf.apng?t=1769466649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/9bf3c42044d1424e7f51002fce2c7acf.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=618 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>管理船只：</strong></i>想要在各种事件及战斗中幸存下来，需要以果断的态度指挥船员，并确保所有船只系统及资源都以最理想的方式使用。证明自己是天生的战略家！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/4a3c31e233882e943fc9fc6c189056ea.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" width=190 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/4a3c31e233882e943fc9fc6c189056ea.webm?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/a149e07c1746245e072b4c5552d3e351.webp?t=1769466649\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/a149e07c1746245e072b4c5552d3e351.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" class=\"bb_img\" width=190 height=80 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>构筑战术牌组：</strong></i>在激烈的战斗中，你将通过一套可构筑并升级战术牌组，指挥船员执行各种行动，并逐步形成自己的游戏风格。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/03cec0fbb3c5c80103dc9d211a4dce64.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/03cec0fbb3c5c80103dc9d211a4dce64.webm?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/03cec0fbb3c5c80103dc9d211a4dce64.mp4?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>沉浸式叙事：</strong></i>《赤海狂盗》呈现了一个由众多岛屿组成的复杂群岛，这里盘踞着冒险家、不法之徒、寻宝者，当然还有普通民众。你将驾驶船只从一座岛屿前往另一座岛屿，与不同的事件交互，并逐步了解这个地方、这里的人们，以及世代海盗所追寻传奇宝藏的故事。你的行为将塑造自己的故事走向，引领你走向不同的且充满危险的——道路。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/6809cbf3afc1f0a0e36d9620484d68b2.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/6809cbf3afc1f0a0e36d9620484d68b2.webm?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/6809cbf3afc1f0a0e36d9620484d68b2.mp4?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>海盗巢穴：</i></strong>在每局游戏中，你将选择一名独一无二的船长和一艘船只来进行指挥。这些海域充满了危险，而你的贪婪很有可能最终会让你葬身海底……但这并不会阻止你再次尝试，重新选择一名海盗船长！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/2d7a38963e4a68e9da7feaf24e6263c3.poster.avif?t=1769466649\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/2d7a38963e4a68e9da7feaf24e6263c3.webm?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/2d7a38963e4a68e9da7feaf24e6263c3.mp4?t=1769466649\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200220/extras/f7274bf3f3d1f33ba1e4daeb3532d6f3.webp?t=1769466649\" width=724 height=40 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
